{"tid":1745102,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧炳強: 足夠人手派駐區選票站　警員票站附近高姿態巡邏","createTime":"2019-11-22T05:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T08:17:38.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c66935df9c08ab9b51148ea3f0f7211c4c32859f","tid":1745102,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:10:16.000Z","msg":"有報道指，星期日區選會選舉當日，警方會派防暴警察駐守票站。新任警務處處長鄧炳強表示，警方會有足夠人手派駐票站，亦會安排警員在票站附近地區作高姿態巡邏，強調香港大部分市民也希望星期日可以和平投票，呼籲投票日不要有不當和暴力行為，否則是與香港700萬人對著幹。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強表示，選舉當日會因應不同的風險評估，安排不同的人手處理，警方亦已作好準備和有不同預案，應付有機會出現的情況，會確保區議會選舉不受干擾，他相信，星期日市民能和平安全地投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493843-20191122.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493843-20191122.htm&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylhfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=904dda7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493843-20191122.htm&h=2d0b590e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493843-20191122.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3fa90206de8b118f5b3f448cd77c2331b6e6a6fe","tid":1745102,"uid":50744,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:13:07.000Z","msg":"傻強:所有警員會喺投票室內保護市民安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb8b9039f9210e9142e2686cbfc2141fb23da9c","tid":1745102,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fa90206de8b118f5b3f448cd77c2331b6e6a6fe","tid":1745102,"uid":50744,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:13:07.000Z","msg":"傻強:所有警員會喺投票室內保護市民安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4169cf7ed145361bdc565d2f6d9d1d23881ab641","tid":1745102,"uid":1215